name: The History of the Seattle Mariners
original_name: The History of the Seattle Mariners
overview: Every team has its highs and lows, frustration, heartbreak, greatness and confusion, but no other team is like this one. The Seattle Mariners are eminently lovable, profoundly human and stunningly, outrageously weird. There is no more fascinating team across the entire history of American sports. This is a six-part SB Nation documentary series created by Jon Bois and Alex Rubenstein.
